{"type":"message","id":"3fabaa4a","parentId":"e03168e7","timestamp":"2026-02-15T10:22:23.548Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 12:22 GMT+2] CLEANUP & TRADE LOGIC (Pro Stream).\n\n1.  **Immediate Cleanup:**\n    *   Delete `C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_dmarket_bot`.\n    *   (Optional) If confident, delete `skills/internal`. I (Pro) confirm: I don't need old prompts. I have `AGENTS.md` in root workspace and my own `CORE_PROTOCOLS_2026.md`.\n\n2.  **PowerShell Syntax Update (Internal Memory):**\n    *   *Self-Correction:* Stop using `&&`. Use `;` or `if ($?) { ... }`.\n    *   *Action:* Verify current session is using `pwsh` correctly.\n\n3.  **Trade Logic (Draft `trade_logic.py`):**\n    *   Create `C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main\\src\\dmarket\\trade_logic.py`.\n    *   Import `dmarket_api`.\n    *   Implement `class TradeManager`.\n    *   Method `monitor_prices(game_id=\"a8db\", threshold_price=5.0)`:\n        *   Call `api.get_market_prices(game_id)`.\n        *   Loop through items.\n        *   Compare price < threshold.\n        *   Log \"Potential Buy: {item_name} at {price}\".\n    *   *Constraint:* Use Type Hints and Docstrings (Google Style).\n\n4.  **Flash Validation:**\n    *   Spawn Flash sub-agent to review `trade_logic.py`.\n    *   Check for Python 3.14 syntax/cleanliness.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Cleanup confirmation.\n    *   Validated `trade_logic.py` content."}],"timestamp":1771150943545}}
{"type":"message","id":"95d51a8e","parentId":"3fabaa4a","timestamp":"2026-02-15T10:22:29.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Defining the Scope**\n\nI'm focused on understanding the user's intent. It seems they want me to handle bot-related tasks, specifically cleanup, syntax correction, and code generation within the context of a DMarket trading bot. My first step is to clarify the scope, starting with the deletion of a specific directory.\n\n\n**Confirming Task Breakdown**\n\nI've got the tasks broken down now. First, delete the specified directory. Then, move on to deleting the `skills/internal` directory, as the user confirmed. I'll need to figure out the right commands to execute these deletions accurately.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"I will start by cleaning up the specified directories and verifying the PowerShell environment. Then I'll draft the `trade_logic.py` file.\n\nFirst, I'll remove the temporary directory and the internal skills folder as requested.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771150949421_298","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Remove-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_dmarket_bot\" -Recurse -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; Remove-Item -Path \"skills/internal\" -Recurse -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; $PSVersionTable"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":5252,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":5455,"cost":{"input":0.010504,"output":0.0024360000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01294}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771150943548}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf5f336f","parentId":"95d51a8e","timestamp":"2026-02-15T10:22:29.653Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec_1771150949421_298","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Name                           Value                                                                                   \r\n----                           -----                                                                                   \r\nPSVersion                      5.1.26100.7705                                                                          \r\nPSEdition                      Desktop                                                                                 \r\nPSCompatibleVersions           {1.0, 2.0, 3.0, 4.0...}                                                                 \r\nBuildVersion                   10.0.26100.7705                                                                         \r\nCLRVersion                     4.0.30319.42000                                                                         \r\nWSManStackVersion              3.0                                                                                     \r\nPSRemotingProtocolVersion      2.3                                                                                     \r\nSerializationVersion           1.1.0.1"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":220,"aggregated":"Name                           Value                                                                                   \r\n----                           -----                                                                                   \r\nPSVersion                      5.1.26100.7705                                                                          \r\nPSEdition                      Desktop                                                                                 \r\nPSCompatibleVersions           {1.0, 2.0, 3.0, 4.0...}             